{"tha-ap530:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap530:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap530:0.3":"Bodhisammajjakattheraapadana ","tha-ap530:1.1":"“Aham pure bodhipattam, ","tha-ap530:1.2":"ujjhitam cetiyangane; ","tha-ap530:1.3":"Tam gahetvana chaddesim, ","tha-ap530:1.4":"alabhim visatigune. ","tha-ap530:2.1":"Tassa kammassa tejena, ","tha-ap530:2.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:2.3":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap530:2.4":"devatte capi manuse. ","tha-ap530:3.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap530:3.2":"agantva manusam bhavam; ","tha-ap530:3.3":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap530:3.4":"khattiye capi brahmane. ","tha-ap530:4.1":"Angapaccangasampanno, ","tha-ap530:4.2":"arohaparinahava; ","tha-ap530:4.3":"Abhirupo suci homi, ","tha-ap530:4.4":"sampunnango anunako. ","tha-ap530:5.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap530:5.2":"jato va yattha katthaci; ","tha-ap530:5.3":"Bhave suvannavanno ca, ","tha-ap530:5.4":"uttattakanakupamo. ","tha-ap530:6.1":"Muduka maddava sniddha, ","tha-ap530:6.2":"sukhuma sukumarika; ","tha-ap530:6.3":"Chavi me sabbada hoti, ","tha-ap530:6.4":"bodhipatte suchaddite. ","tha-ap530:7.1":"Yato kutoci gatisu, ","tha-ap530:7.2":"sarire samudagate; ","tha-ap530:7.3":"Na limpati rajojallam, ","tha-ap530:7.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:8.1":"Unhe vatatape tassa, ","tha-ap530:8.2":"aggitapena va pana; ","tha-ap530:8.3":"Gatte seda na muccanti, ","tha-ap530:8.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:9.1":"Kuttham gando kilaso ca, ","tha-ap530:9.2":"tilaka pilaka tatha; ","tha-ap530:9.3":"Na honti kaye daddu ca, ","tha-ap530:9.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:10.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:10.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:10.3":"Roga na honti kayasmim, ","tha-ap530:10.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:11.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:11.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:11.3":"Na hoti cittaja pila, ","tha-ap530:11.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:12.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:12.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:12.3":"Amitta na bhavantassa, ","tha-ap530:12.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:13.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:13.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:13.3":"Anunabhogo bhavati, ","tha-ap530:13.4":"vipako pattachaddite. ","tha-ap530:14.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:14.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:14.3":"Aggirajuhi corehi, ","tha-ap530:14.4":"na hoti udake bhayam. ","tha-ap530:15.1":"Aparampi gunam tassa, ","tha-ap530:15.2":"nibbattati bhavabhave; ","tha-ap530:15.3":"Dasidasa anucara, ","tha-ap530:15.4":"honti cittanuvattaka. ","tha-ap530:16.1":"Yamhi ayuppamanamhi, ","tha-ap530:16.2":"jayate manuse bhave; ","tha-ap530:16.3":"Tato na hayate ayu, ","tha-ap530:16.4":"titthate yavatayukam. ","tha-ap530:17.1":"Abbhantara ca bahira, ","tha-ap530:17.2":"negama ca saratthaka; ","tha-ap530:17.3":"Nuyutta honti sabbepi, ","tha-ap530:17.4":"vuddhikama sukhicchaka. ","tha-ap530:18.1":"Bhogava yasava homi, ","tha-ap530:18.2":"sirima natipakkhava; ","tha-ap530:18.3":"Apetabhayasantaso, ","tha-ap530:18.4":"bhaveham sabbato bhave. ","tha-ap530:19.1":"Deva manussa asura, ","tha-ap530:19.2":"gandhabba yakkharakkhasa; ","tha-ap530:19.3":"Sabbe te parirakkhanti, ","tha-ap530:19.4":"bhave samsarato sada. ","tha-ap530:20.1":"Devaloke manusse ca, ","tha-ap530:20.2":"anubhotva ubho yase; ","tha-ap530:20.3":"Avasane ca nibbanam, ","tha-ap530:20.4":"sivam patto anuttaram. ","tha-ap530:21.1":"Sambuddhamuddisitvana, ","tha-ap530:21.2":"bodhim va tassa satthuno; ","tha-ap530:21.3":"Yo punnam pasave poso, ","tha-ap530:21.4":"tassa kim nama dullabham. ","tha-ap530:22.1":"Magge phale agame ca, ","tha-ap530:22.2":"jhanabhinnagunesu ca; ","tha-ap530:22.3":"Annesam adhiko hutva, ","tha-ap530:22.4":"nibbayami anasavo. ","tha-ap530:23.1":"Pureham bodhiya pattam, ","tha-ap530:23.2":"chaddetva hatthamanaso; ","tha-ap530:23.3":"Imehi visatangehi, ","tha-ap530:23.4":"samangi homi sabbada. ","tha-ap530:24.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap530:24.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap530:24.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap530:25.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap530:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap530:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap530:26.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap530:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap530:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap530:27.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bodhisammajjako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap530:28.1":"Bodhisammajjakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}